Package: Distributacalcul
Type: Package
Title: Probability distribution functions
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Alec James", "van Rassel", email = "alec.van-rassel.1@ulaval.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
  person("Gabriel", "Cr√©peault-Cauchon", role = c("aut"))
 )
Description: Calculates expected values, variance, different moments (k-th moment, truncated expected value), stop-loss, excess of mean, Value at Risk (VaR) and Tail Value at Risk (TVaR) as well as the density and cumulative/survival functions of continuous, discrete and compound distributions.
